<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Rotation on Balance Guides</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/tags/rotation/</link><description>Recent content in Rotation on Balance Guides</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Aug 2025 19:00:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/tags/rotation/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Paladin Basics Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/paladin/basic-guide/</link><pubDate>Wed, 06 Aug 2025 19:00:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/paladin/basic-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p>Welcome to the Basics Guide for Paladin! Whether you are a fresh level 100, a returning player, or just need a refresher, this guide will get you started and allow you to hit the ground running.&lt;/p>
